snippet.title: edepot
snippet.description:
edepot YouTube: Advanced Gaming Channel. 

For popular games like:
Cyberpunk 2077
Red Dead Redemption 2 (RDR2)
Metal Gear Solid V: Phantom Pain
Final Fantasy XV
Death Stranding
The Last of Us Part II
God of War (2018)
Ghost of Tsushima
Animal Crossing: New Horizons
Assassin's Creed Origins
Spider-Man
Alien: Isolation
Horizon Zero Dawn
Dying Light

 Skillful gameplays and walkthroughs also available.

Also includes a selection of interesting technology, fashion models, culture, and things to balance out gaming. If there was one channel you should join, THIS IS IT! See fun stuff (highest skyscraper observation deck views, toys, illusions, funny videos, and cute pets and animals like rabbits and dogs), cultural stuff (lots of videos from asian culture fashion models, anime, drawing, origami, buddhism, taoism, famous places, etc). There are just too many good things to see that you have to join to appreciate!
